      <title>美联储戴利：通胀下降之际必须保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-15/fed-s-daly-must-stay-vigilant-as-inflation-declines-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽·戴利表示，美国央行“必须保持警惕，并有意识地采取行动”，全面实现 2% 的通胀目标，同时确保劳动力市场保持充分就业。戴利周二在纽约大学斯特恩商学院举办的一场活动上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-15/fed-s-daly-must-stay-vigilant-as-inflation-declines-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对昂贵手袋的需求下降导致 LVMH 销售额下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/lvmh-quarterly-sales-drop-as-demand-cools-for-costly-handbags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着过去一年中国奢侈品需求回落的规模愈加明显，LVMH 旗下最大品牌的销售额自 2020 年以来首次出现意外下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/lvmh-quarterly-sales-drop-as-demand-cools-for-costly-handbags</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:49:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>强生首席财务官沃克谈产品线、战略、滑石粉诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-15/j-j-cfo-wolk-on-product-pipeline-strategy-talc-lawsuit-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强生公司首席财务官 Joseph Wolk 在“彭博未平仓合约”上讨论了公司的产品线、收购策略以及滑石粉婴儿爽身粉诉讼的最新进展。强生公司报告称，受抗癌药物 Darzalex 销售激增的推动，第三季度收益强于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-15/j-j-cfo-wolk-on-product-pipeline-strategy-talc-lawsuit-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Holcim 考虑将价值 300 亿美元的美国业务在两地上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/holcim-said-to-consider-dual-listing-of-30-billion-us-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，瑞士建筑公司 Holcim Ltd. 正在考虑将其北美子公司在美国和瑞士双重上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/holcim-said-to-consider-dual-listing-of-30-billion-us-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:32:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币价格在创下 7 月以来最高水平后回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/bitcoin-tops-67-000-to-reach-highest-level-since-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币两个多月来首次突破 67,000 美元，但随着美国大选临近，数字资产领域波动性加剧，比特币价格很快抹去了涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/bitcoin-tops-67-000-to-reach-highest-level-since-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 14:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
